{"tid":60480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2016十大笑爆黃洋達事件","createTime":"2016-12-30T13:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T14:56:48.000Z","uid":67558,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5125cb034551cdd4aa81cdd54535de496a9dee9e","tid":60480,"uid":67558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:02:45.000Z","msg":"第十位：用YouTube做直播，在線人數即刻現形少十倍。<br />\n第九位：以衝擊中聯辦係ON9行為去解釋熱時零報導。<br />\n第八位：熱時年宵攤位拍烏蠅，隔離100毛就大排長龍。<br />\n第七位：懶理柏洋入獄，黃洋達夫婦笠垃圾袋遊山玩水。<br />\n第六位：張德江到港，為掩飾怕死，黃洋達話唔L理佢。<br />\n第五位：驚冇得選，搶簽確認書，點知民主派個個唔簽。<br />\n第四位：安全才出動，黃洋達率眾去日領抗議任天堂。<br />\n第三位：被多人秒殺，黃洋達選舉論壇醜態百出。<br />\n第二位：黃洋達台灣示範勇武燒中國旗。<br />\n第一位：立法會兩連敗，黃洋達一路走來，始終唔得。<img src=\"http://holland.pk/8lj9v1eu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8lj9v1eu.jpg&h=a3a568d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33864ecfb4398a99c1b7535afa39596d708edc2","tid":60480,"uid":67558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8lj9v1eu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8lj9v1eu&h=b3f696b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a56d069937f901fcbeedc2f596244c4e92e753","tid":60480,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da030067a123885a59957e1dc1ce8561283011c","tid":60480,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0